{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_016zUNiUtHcX69q2FCZAxNS5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"TLS leaf certificate rotation is complete and verified. Summary:\n\n**What was found:** the `rabbitmq-tls`/`rabbitmq-tls-ca` secrets existed with a near-expiry leaf (expired the next day), but TLS was never actually wired into the running cluster — no `listeners.ssl` in `rabbitmq.conf`, no secret mounted into the pods, no 5671 port anywhere. So the fix required both rotating the cert and enabling TLS for real.\n\n**Actions taken (native resources only):**\n1. Pulled `ca.key` (from `rabbitmq-tls-ca`) and `ca.crt`/old leaf (from `rabbitmq-tls`), verified the key matches the CA cert.\n2. Generated a new 2048-bit RSA leaf key/CSR with the same CN/SANs as the old leaf, signed it with the existing CA for 60 days (well over the 30-day minimum).\n3. Patched the `rabbitmq-tls` Secret in place with the new `tls.crt`/`tls.key`, leaving `ca.crt` untouched.\n4. Added `listeners.ssl.default = 5671` + `ssl_options.*` to the `rabbitmq-config` ConfigMap, mounted the `rabbitmq-tls` secret into the StatefulSet at `/etc/rabbitmq/tls`, added the `amqp-tls` container port, and exposed 5671 on both Services.\n5. Watched the StatefulSet's rolling update (`OrderedReady`, one pod at a time) complete — all 3 pods came back `1/1 Running`, 0 restarts.\n\n**Verified:**\n- `rabbitmqctl cluster_status`: all 3 nodes up, no alarms, no partitions, each with an `amqp/ssl` listener on 5671.\n- `openssl s_client` from the `openssl-toolbox` pod against `rabbitmq` and all 3 per-pod DNS names: handshake succeeds, `Verify return code: 0 (ok)` against the CA.\n- Served leaf cert: `notAfter=Aug 30 2026` (60 days out), same on all 3 nodes.\n- CA fingerprint unchanged (`74:8B:89:...` matches the pre-rotation baseline in `rabbitmq-tls-old`); leaf fingerprint changed (`DE:14:33:...` → `04:93:33:...`).\n- `app-producer` kept running with no new errors; plain AMQP (5672) and management (15672) unaffected."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":191,"cache_read_input_tokens":86911,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":191},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"99737840-1618-43a3-ab9c-68498e32bec9","uuid":"5797f030-cb3b-4244-a0e4-ad75b953ebfd","request_id":"req_011Ccar3vjPnu2vVQJN19xpM"}
